> $ AXIOMsys
> dyld: Library not loaded: /home/users/b/bi/billpage/osx/lib/libintl.=20
> 8.dylib
>    Referenced from: /Users/raym/Desktop/powerpc-apple-darwin6.8/bin/=20
> AXIOMsys
>    Reason: image not found
> Trace/BPT trap
>=20
> 	So some remaining path problems I fear...
