I don't if it is of any help, see ax.boot:

     axOpTran(name) ==
        ATOM name =>
           name = 'elt => 'apply
           name = 'setelt => 'set!
           name = 'SEGMENT => ".."
           name = 1 => '_1
           name = 0 => '_0
           name
        opOf name = 'Zero => '_0
        opOf name = 'One => '_1
        error "bad op name"

-- gaby



