Hi, 

opening on a not very current FreeBSD using Mozilla fails with the request 
to download plugins.
However, direct download of the mov/avi (e.g. fetch 
http://daly.axiom-developer.org/literate/MakeAxiom_mov/MakeAxiom_mov_media/M 
