I'm going to suppress the Juergen Weiss's asec definition.

And just for the fun, here is its definition :

#+:(or :cmu :akcl :gcl)
(defun asec (a)
  (if (and (a > -1.0) (a < 1.0))
    0.0
    (acos (/ 1.0 a))))

And no one sees the errors :-)

Greg




