--- wh-sandbox.bb/src/interp/alql.boot.pamphlet	2006-11-30 01:00:42.000000000 +0100
+++ wh-sandbox/src/interp/alql.boot.pamphlet	2006-12-01 02:14:24.000000000 +0100
