             ((NULL (MEMBER |k1| (LIST '|o| '|k| '|c| '|d| '|p|))) NIL)

are still not explained to me.

| 'member' user 'EQUAL' on strings.  'MEMBER' uses 'EQ', which does not
| give expected effect for strings.

